-And cute.

01:12:34.483 --> 01:12:36.974
Look, Grace, I'm sorry.
I just can't do that.

01:12:54.136 --> 01:12:55.694
You turned her down, didn't you?

01:12:58.107 --> 01:12:59.506
Mickey's good boy.

01:13:06.181 --> 01:13:10.618
Sainthood.
Is that what you're going for?

01:13:25.401 --> 01:13:26.959
It's going to be a fine trip.

01:13:27.102 --> 01:13:29.730
