01:13:47.589 --> 01:13:50.581
He's a damn fine bargaining chip.
You could jump a few rooms.

01:13:51.427 --> 01:13:53.224
Do you know what the word
"collusion" means?

01:13:54.329 --> 01:13:56.729
Although, it does have a certain
romantic ring to it...

01:13:56.865 --> 01:13:59.168
but as words go, it's extremely
