01:13:59.168 --> 01:14:01.864
It means we're doing the dirty work
while those brave souls in London...

01:14:01.970 --> 01:14:04.200
fight a battle from their
fucking drawing rooms.

01:14:05.140 --> 01:14:08.769
I'm telling you, I like it here.
It's, like, peaceful. It's nice.

01:14:09.778 --> 01:14:12.508
Look around, right? There's not one
chopper overhead, nothing.

01:14:12.614 --> 01:14:13.239
It's nice.

01:14:13.882 --> 01:14:17.147
I guess you're nesting. Come on.
we're late.

01:14:17.719 --> 01:14:20.085
I'm just letting you know, you're
not going in on your own, okay?

01:14:20.222 --> 01:14:21.280
I'll do what I need to do.

01:14:27.729 --> 01:14:31.187
Grace, good to see you.
Apologies about the cold boys, eh?

01:14:31.200 --> 01:14:33.259
So why are you wearing
that naff jumper then?

01:14:34.203 --> 01:14:35.602
what the fuck is wrong with you?

01:14:36.472 --> 01:14:37.302
Bastard!

01:14:40.075 --> 01:14:41.474
I told you no guns.

01:14:41.543 --> 01:14:43.306
Are we going to do
this deal, or what?

01:14:46.014 --> 01:14:49.279
Grace, you're not going in
on your own, okay?

01:15:01.930 --> 01:15:03.761
For fuck's sake.

01:15:06.134 --> 01:15:08.728
I'll be looking into you.
You can count on it.

01:15:10.138 --> 01:15:10.797
Lara?

01:15:12.674 --> 01:15:13.299
Lara?

01:15:31.159 --> 01:15:33.992
-ls she here?
-Three days and nights you disappear?

01:15:34.062 --> 01:15:36.587
I know, I know. Look, can I just
speak to her, Mrs. Flaherty, please?

01:15:36.665 --> 01:15:37.495
Oh, shame on you!

01:15:37.533 --> 01:15:39.057
I just need to speak to her
for just a wee second!

01:15:39.167 --> 01:15:41.226
-Keep away from her...
-Lara! Lara, are you in there?

01:15:41.336 --> 01:15:44.305
-No, please, I was snagged by the RUC!
-Oh, yes, that's a good one!

01:15:44.339 --> 01:15:46.136
They wouldn't let me near a telephone!

01:15:46.241 --> 01:15:48.709
I swear, Lara, they wouldn't
let me near a telephone!

01:15:48.810 --> 01:15:50.505
There was nothing I could do!

01:15:50.612 --> 01:15:53.706
If I could have spoken to you, I would!
Come on, please!

01:15:54.249 --> 01:15:57.184
will you just come to the window, Lara?
Please, I just want to see your face!

01:15:57.252 --> 01:15:58.685
Please, Lara!

01:15:59.254 --> 01:16:00.084
Fuck...

01:16:01.256 --> 01:16:02.348
Lara, please.

01:16:08.096 --> 01:16:10.462
I'm so sorry.
Lara, I'm sorry.

01:16:13.635 --> 01:16:14.567
I'm sorry.

01:16:17.639 --> 01:16:19.903
I'm so sorry.
I'm so sorry.

01:16:21.910 --> 01:16:23.138
I'm sorry.

01:16:24.713 --> 01:16:28.479
I love you, okay?
